.Ss MPI OPTIONS
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width "--concatenate" -compact
.It Fl P Ar file
.It Fl -partition-file Ar file
Specifies the
.Ar partition
file which contains one exodus file per line. These exodus files will be used for training.
Each exodus file, or partition, is processed independently.
.El
.Pp
NOTE: See the
.Sx FILENAMES
section for details on what files are used for what purpose.
.Pp
NOTE: The partition file may contain a single exodus file.
